and that poor kid just began to unravel.

206
00:08:01.516 --> 00:08:02.841
It became really difficult,

207
00:08:02.841 --> 00:08:05.798
and I remember one night he tried to kill me,

208
00:08:05.798 --> 00:08:09.834
and the police took him away and he was on probation.

209
00:08:09.834 --> 00:08:12.348
And through probation,

210
00:08:12.348 --> 00:08:15.348
I was actually offered a job to work Juvenile Probation,

211
00:08:15.348 --> 00:08:17.388
down in Maricopa County.

212
00:08:17.388 --> 00:08:19.497
So I actually worked probation for a while

213
00:08:19.497 --> 00:08:21.492
until then I was offered a position,

214
00:08:21.492 --> 00:08:23.444
someone approached me and said,

215
00:08:23.444 --> 00:08:25.460
"You apparently work real well with teenage boys,

216
00:08:25.460 --> 00:08:28.169
we've got a lot of boys who need a father figure."

217
00:08:28.169 --> 00:08:30.258
And like you said, I've always wanted to be a parent

218
00:08:30.258 --> 00:08:33.039
in an unconventional way without the wife,

219
00:08:33.039 --> 00:08:35.973
so I knew right away, this is something that I need to do.

220
00:08:35.973 --> 00:08:37.907
And through the adoption of my first son

221
00:08:37.907 --> 00:08:39.133
several years prior to that,

222
00:08:39.133 --> 00:08:41.510
I knew that this is the way to go.

223
00:08:41.510 --> 00:08:43.118
So I left Juvenile Probation

224
00:08:43.118 --> 00:08:45.127
and became a therapeutic foster parent.

225
00:08:45.127 --> 00:08:47.614
And the difference between therapeutic and regular

226
00:08:47.614 --> 00:08:49.820
is the children who do not qualify

227
00:08:49.820 --> 00:08:51.874
for regular foster care because of their

228
00:08:51.874 --> 00:08:54.021
therapeutic needs and their diagnoses

229
00:08:54.021 --> 00:08:56.144
are in specialized trained homes

230
00:08:56.144 --> 00:08:58.025
with therapeutic foster parents.

231
00:08:58.025 --> 00:09:01.869
Who require to be home 24/7 to be with these kids.

232
00:09:01.869 --> 00:09:03.859
That's the direction my life took,

233
00:09:03.859 --> 00:09:07.087
and suddenly the kids began to find me,

234
00:09:07.087 --> 00:09:10.350
and today I have seven children.

235
00:09:10.755 --> 00:09:13.507
<v ->And we'll talk about one of them in a moment.</v>

236
00:09:13.507 --> 00:09:16.726
So you have three adopted children and three foster children

237
00:09:16.726 --> 00:09:18.681
right now.
<v ->That's right.</v>

238
00:09:19.038 --> 00:09:21.850
<v ->These kids that found their way to you,</v>

239
00:09:22.599 --> 00:09:24.637
to say that each one of them has challenges

240
00:09:24.637 --> 00:09:27.552
would be fair, if not an understatement?

241
00:09:27.552 --> 00:09:29.286
<v ->Absolutely.</v>

242
00:09:31.973 --> 00:09:33.658
<v ->What did this journey do to you?</v>

243
00:09:33.658 --> 00:09:36.307
Here you, in your own life are struggling

244
00:09:36.307 --> 00:09:39.774
to keep your own spirits intact

245
00:09:39.774 --> 00:09:41.619
and your will intact,

246
00:09:41.619 --> 00:09:44.036
and then bring in these children,

247
00:09:44.036 --> 00:09:47.275
or attract these children to you that need help as badly.

248
00:09:47.275 --> 00:09:49.040
If not more than you.

249
00:09:49.040 --> 00:09:53.052
What happened in that whole dynamic the last few years?

250
00:09:53.052 --> 00:09:54.558
<v ->I think</v>

251
00:09:56.465 --> 00:09:59.655
to encase this entire scenario is to say that

252
00:09:59.655 --> 00:10:01.464
I've always been a truth seeker and I've been looking

253
00:10:01.464 --> 00:10:03.077
for all these answers that we all ask,

254
00:10:03.077 --> 00:10:04.050
why am I here?

255
00:10:04.050 --> 00:10:04.946
What is my purpose?

256
00:10:04.946 --> 00:10:05.970
Where am I going?

257
00:10:05.970 --> 00:10:07.476
Where did I come from?

258
00:10:07.476 --> 00:10:10.528
In the back of my mind I'd always ask those questions.

259
00:10:10.528 --> 00:10:13.450
And through my difficult life being gay and in the military,

260
00:10:13.450 --> 00:10:14.839
and the things I'd experience,

261
00:10:14.839 --> 00:10:16.497
it seems as though then I began once again

262
00:10:16.497 --> 00:10:19.826
to attract myself through these other children

