00:10:19.826 --> 00:10:21.607
and the issues that they have.

264
00:10:21.607 --> 00:10:24.401
My children, they range from gay, to straight,

265
00:10:24.401 --> 00:10:26.813
to black, white, Hispanic,

266
00:10:27.021 --> 00:10:30.744
just multicultural, multifaceted, multi-dynamic.

267
00:10:30.744 --> 00:10:33.637
Their problems are all so unique but they're all difficult

268
00:10:33.637 --> 00:10:35.927
issues that these children have to deal with.

269
00:10:35.927 --> 00:10:38.372
And I see parts of myself in all my kids.

270
00:10:38.372 --> 00:10:41.061
And my kids respond a lot to the way I am,

271
00:10:41.061 --> 00:10:43.270
your children respond to the energy that the parent

272
00:10:43.270 --> 00:10:44.317
puts forth.

273
00:10:44.317 --> 00:10:46.238
So when the parent is very centered and stabled,

274
00:10:46.238 --> 00:10:49.040
and peaceful and calm, you'll reflect that and the children

275
00:10:49.040 --> 00:10:52.599
will feed that and you'll see that in them.

276
00:10:52.599 --> 00:10:55.945
But if you're going through depression and difficult times,

277
00:10:55.945 --> 00:10:58.453
boy your kids are gonna reflect that.

278
00:10:58.453 --> 00:11:01.597
In the last five years I really began to view life

279
00:11:01.597 --> 00:11:02.984
as a living hell,

280
00:11:02.984 --> 00:11:05.787
and it was just a horrible place that we were sent to,

281
00:11:05.787 --> 00:11:07.589
and I wanted to leave.

282
00:11:07.589 --> 00:11:09.855
So many horrible things were happening.

283
00:11:09.855 --> 00:11:13.250
I had severe financial issues

284
00:11:13.250 --> 00:11:16.522
as a result of one of my children's hospitalizations,

285
00:11:16.522 --> 00:11:19.432
and being sent to a residential treatment center.

286
00:11:19.432 --> 00:11:22.904
Another child who got into crystal meth

287
00:11:22.904 --> 00:11:24.615
and nearly killed himself,

288
00:11:24.615 --> 00:11:26.125
I got him through drug treatment.

289
00:11:26.125 --> 00:11:27.811
Things were just coming at me.

290
00:11:27.811 --> 00:11:30.102
I was being barraged by these things.

291
00:11:30.102 --> 00:11:32.930
Then last year, I think the ultimate hit me,

292
00:11:32.930 --> 00:11:35.847
and that was the night my son Ryan died in my arms

293
00:11:35.847 --> 00:11:36.937
at home,

294
00:11:36.937 --> 00:11:38.948
so unexpectedly.

295
00:11:38.948 --> 00:11:42.132
Within five to seven minutes you had a happy child,

296
00:11:42.132 --> 00:11:43.526
and then he was gone.

297
00:11:43.526 --> 00:11:45.001
<v ->What happened?</v>

298
00:11:45.161 --> 00:11:49.006
<v ->I remember it was Easter Sunday, March 27th 2005.</v>

299
00:11:49.006 --> 00:11:51.109
I was watching television in the living room,

300
00:11:51.109 --> 00:11:53.424
my son Ryan was in the bedroom talking on the phone

301
00:11:53.424 --> 00:11:54.641
with a friend,

302
00:11:54.641 --> 00:11:58.303
and he was carving a lid for a goldfish bowl.

303
00:11:58.303 --> 00:12:00.761
He had just gotten a pet frog that day,

304
00:12:00.761 --> 00:12:03.795
and he wanted to put a lid on it to protect it from the cat.

305
00:12:03.795 --> 00:12:05.983
As he was carving it he had the container held

306
00:12:05.983 --> 00:12:07.199
against his chest,

307
00:12:07.199 --> 00:12:08.897
and as he was poking holes into it

308
00:12:08.897 --> 00:12:10.356
the container collapsed,

309
00:12:10.356 --> 00:12:13.044
and the knife went directly into his heart.

310
00:12:13.044 --> 00:12:15.299
And he told his friend on the phone,

311
00:12:15.299 --> 00:12:17.601
"Oh shoot, I just cut myself, I gotta go,"

312
00:12:17.601 --> 00:12:21.567
threw the phone down, pulled the knife out of his heart.

313
00:12:21.567 --> 00:12:23.899
I remember he picked up a sock, covered it with a sock

314
00:12:23.899 --> 00:12:25.020
and came to me and says,

315
00:12:25.020 --> 00:12:26.309
"Dad, I cut myself.

316
00:12:26.309 --> 00:12:27.362
I need help."

317
00:12:27.362 --> 00:12:29.322
And I thought, well lemme get the first aid kit,

318
00:12:29.322 --> 00:12:31.445
'cause boys were always hurtin' themselves

319
00:12:31.445 --> 00:12:33.047
from rough play.

320
00:12:33.047 --> 00:12:35.069
I saw the blood trickling down his chest

321
00:12:35.069 --> 00:12:37.273
and I took him into the bathroom and put a compress on it,

322
00:12:37.273 --> 00:12:40.294
mind you, I was a paramedic for eight years in the military,

323
00:12:40.294 --> 00:12:42.854
so I thought I had a pretty good grasp on what to do.

324
00:12:42.854 --> 00:12:45.064
Few minutes later, he had his arms around me, he says,

325
00:12:45.064 --> 00:12:47.511
"Dad, I'm gonna faint, I'm gonna pass out."

326
00:12:47.511 --> 00:12:49.188
And down he went like a load of bricks.

327
00:12:49.188 --> 00:12:51.748
His glasses flew off, his head hit the toilet,

328
00:12:51.748 --> 00:12:53.156
he was just floundering in my arms

329
00:12:53.156 --> 00:12:56.202
and I screamed and called for my other son to help me.

330
00:12:56.202 --> 00:12:58.795
He came in, I said you gotta help me, Ryan's hurt.

331
00:12:58.795 --> 00:13:00.931
I've gotta call 911.

332
00:13:01.125 --> 00:13:04.014
And after I called 911 and Ryan was laying on the ground,

333
00:13:04.014 --> 00:13:05.359
on the floor in the bathroom,

334
00:13:05.359 --> 00:13:07.145
he just opened his eyes, looked at me and says,

335
00:13:07.145 --> 00:13:09.243
"Dad, I'm okay, I'm okay."

336
00:13:09.243 --> 00:13:10.856
Then he closed his eyes,

337
00:13:10.856 --> 00:13:13.054
his eyes then rolled back, his arms twitched,

338
00:13:13.054 --> 00:13:14.603
he went into shock,

339
00:13:14.603 --> 00:13:16.932
and I picked him up, carried him to the living room

340
00:13:16.932 --> 00:13:18.417
waiting for the paramedics.

341
00:13:18.417 --> 00:13:21.150
And while I was holding him, he passed away.

342
00:13:21.540 --> 00:13:24.712
It was just so surreal, it happened so quickly.

343
00:13:24.712 --> 00:13:27.454
I couldn't process it all, I was in shock.

344
00:13:27.454 --> 00:13:30.283
Of course that began a long period of time

345
00:13:30.283 --> 00:13:31.895
for my family and I

346
00:13:31.895 --> 00:13:35.833
for going through the process of disbelief and denial,

347
00:13:35.833 --> 00:13:38.550
and shock, to getting to the point of acceptance

348
00:13:38.550 --> 00:13:39.994
that he was gone so quickly.

349
00:13:39.994 --> 00:13:44.134
<v ->How did that affect you on the deepest levels,</v>

350
00:13:44.358 --> 00:13:47.597
in that you had considered taking your own life

351
00:13:47.597 --> 00:13:50.602
on numerous occasions prior to that as a way

352
00:13:50.602 --> 00:13:54.926
to merge with something more gentle and more kind,

353
00:13:54.926 --> 00:13:57.387
than the world you were experiencing?

354
00:13:57.387 --> 00:14:00.864
How did that all work together in your heart

355
00:14:00.864 --> 00:14:02.182
and in your mind

356
00:14:02.182 --> 00:14:04.885
when here someone who had not chosen to do this,

357
00:14:04.885 --> 00:14:08.050
it was quite by accident, is suddenly gone?

358
00:14:09.054 --> 00:14:10.744
I don't know if that's even a fair question,

359
00:14:10.744 --> 00:14:13.214
it just is coming through my head right now.

360
00:14:13.214 --> 00:14:16.529
<v ->My first thought was how did I attract this into my life?</v>

361
00:14:16.529 --> 00:14:18.129
How did I bring this about?

362
00:14:18.129 --> 00:14:19.665
Course a parent will feel some guilt

363
00:14:19.665 --> 00:14:21.405
that I couldn't protect my child,

364
00:14:21.405 --> 00:14:23.325
that's my job is to protect my child.

365
00:14:23.325 --> 00:14:24.516
But I couldn't do it.

366
00:14:24.516 --> 00:14:28.325
Did I somehow, miraculously draw this into my life?

367
00:14:28.325 --> 00:14:30.278
And I knew right away

368
00:14:30.278 --> 00:14:32.615
there is no guilt, there is no blame,

369
00:14:32.615 --> 00:14:35.253
but why did my son die?

370
00:14:35.253 --> 00:14:38.248
And why did he die at his own hand albeit an accident?

371
00:14:38.248 --> 00:14:39.758
Isn't that the irony?

372
00:14:39.758 --> 00:14:43.047
That I had longed to take my life to find peace and joy,

373
00:14:43.047 --> 00:14:45.927
not just to run from this life but to go somewhere

374
00:14:45.927 --> 00:14:48.910
that was more kind and gentle, as you said.

375
00:14:48.910 --> 00:14:50.343
Here it is my son,

376
00:14:50.343 --> 00:14:53.477
apparently found that place, and why?

377
00:14:53.477 --> 00:14:56.433
I spent a year in talk therapy trying to deal

378
00:14:56.433 --> 00:14:58.553
with these issues.

379
00:14:58.553 --> 00:15:01.842
I began devouring books

380
00:15:01.842 --> 00:15:05.291
on after death and near life experiences,

381
00:15:05.291 --> 00:15:08.287
which actually led me to Conscious Media Network.

382
00:15:08.287 --> 00:15:11.090
In part of my search for answers of why my son died

383
00:15:11.090 --> 00:15:12.677
and where did he go,

384
00:15:12.677 --> 00:15:15.941
I found a number of interviews on Conscious Media Network

385
00:15:15.941 --> 00:15:17.863
that really alleviated the pain.

386
00:15:17.863 --> 00:15:21.894
And helped me to understand that we survive our death.

387
00:15:21.894 --> 00:15:25.398
We don't really die as these infinite beings.

388
00:15:25.398 --> 00:15:28.505
Our bodies pass away as organic substance,

389
00:15:28.505 --> 00:15:32.526
but our living infinite creative being still exists.

390
00:15:32.526 --> 00:15:36.132
And I knew then that my son was still alive,

391
00:15:36.132 --> 00:15:39.471
and often times with me 'cause I felt him with me.

392
00:15:39.821 --> 00:15:42.468
Which made me extremely grateful,

393
00:15:42.468 --> 00:15:45.576
extremely grateful and I can't express how much

394
00:15:46.246 --> 00:15:47.660
comfort that gave me

395
00:15:47.660 --> 00:15:49.983
through your media network.

396
00:15:49.983 --> 00:15:50.829
<v ->Thank you.</v>

397
00:15:50.829 --> 00:15:52.216
<v ->But even greater things were to come.</v>

398
00:15:52.216 --> 00:15:54.188
<v ->Yes.
<v ->As a result.</v>

399
00:15:55.468 --> 00:15:58.017
<v ->This experienced happened, there was a lot of grieving,</v>

400
00:15:58.017 --> 00:15:59.889
a lot to sort through,

401
00:15:59.889 --> 00:16:02.130
but ultimately you started becoming more and more

402
00:16:02.130 --> 00:16:03.105
depressed.

403
00:16:03.105 --> 00:16:03.904
<v ->Yes.</v>

404
00:16:03.904 --> 00:16:05.811
<v ->And tell us what happened from there.</v>

405
00:16:05.811 --> 00:16:08.640
<v ->Well it seemed like it just began a spiral down.</v>

406
00:16:08.640 --> 00:16:11.842
Things got worse and I think I was reliving all those

407
00:16:11.842 --> 00:16:13.341
scenarios in my mind every night.

408
00:16:13.341 --> 00:16:14.797
It's like, oh my god, what if another one

409
00:16:14.797 --> 00:16:15.823
of my children die?

410
00:16:15.823 --> 00:16:16.932
How will I handle it?

411
00:16:16.932 --> 00:16:18.346
I'll take my own life.

412
00:16:18.346 --> 00:16:19.761
There were legal issues with my kids,

413
00:16:19.761 --> 00:16:21.027
medical issues with my kids,

414
00:16:21.027 --> 00:16:22.526
every day it was a barrage,

415
00:16:22.526 --> 00:16:24.369
and I was on this downward spiral.

416
00:16:24.369 --> 00:16:26.378
It was getting worse, it was getting worse.

417
00:16:26.378 --> 00:16:28.196
I had no family and friends in Phoenix,

418
00:16:28.196 --> 00:16:30.237
and I had no support network.

419
00:16:30.237 --> 00:16:31.885
It was just me and my kids,

420
00:16:31.885 --> 00:16:34.544
demanding and draining my energy from me every day,

421
00:16:34.544 --> 00:16:36.852
and I wasn't being replenished.

422
00:16:37.914 --> 00:16:39.033
I had gotten to a point,

423
00:16:39.033 --> 00:16:41.452
it was actually toward the end of July,

424
00:16:41.452 --> 00:16:43.238
and I remember

425
00:16:43.567 --> 00:16:46.507
I began planning my exit from this life.

426
00:16:46.507 --> 00:16:49.086
Now mind you, I don't think I ever wanted to commit suicide

427
00:16:49.086 --> 00:16:52.375
as an end, it was a means to an end,

428
00:16:52.375 --> 00:16:53.834
and the end was peace.

429
00:16:53.834 --> 00:16:56.522
Peace and joy and contentment and happiness,

430
00:16:56.522 --> 00:16:58.301
and all the things that I discovered

