00:16:58.301 --> 00:17:00.349
from people who've written thousands of near death

432
00:17:00.349 --> 00:17:01.666
experiences,

433
00:17:01.666 --> 00:17:03.684
that this is something I really wanted.

434
00:17:03.684 --> 00:17:05.200
It's like, I wanna go to heaven.

435
00:17:05.200 --> 00:17:09.075
I wanna go where life is so wonderful, so peaceful.

436
00:17:09.075 --> 00:17:11.558
There's no fear, no anger, no hatred.

437
00:17:11.558 --> 00:17:14.910
I wanted this so bad that I was willing to commit suicide

438
00:17:14.910 --> 00:17:16.740
in order to gain it.

439
00:17:16.740 --> 00:17:19.428
So I put my plan into action.

440
00:17:19.428 --> 00:17:22.768
I began researching my life insurance policies to ensure

441
00:17:22.768 --> 00:17:24.547
that my kids would get a payout.

442
00:17:24.547 --> 00:17:26.032
I put together a living trust,

443
00:17:26.032 --> 00:17:28.886
I put together my living will, my will.

444
00:17:28.886 --> 00:17:30.968
My do not resuscitate.

