00:17:30.968 --> 00:17:34.721
In fact, it was the 28th of July

446
00:17:34.721 --> 00:17:38.194
where I signed the documentation for the update of my will

447
00:17:38.194 --> 00:17:40.253
to ensure everything was taken care of.

448
00:17:40.253 --> 00:17:41.535
<v ->That was less than a month ago.</v>

449
00:17:41.535 --> 00:17:43.223
<v ->Right, less than a month ago.</v>

