00:17:54.826 --> 00:17:56.362
But I knew that I wouldn't do that because I don't want

456
00:17:56.362 --> 00:17:58.627
my children to see me like that.

457
00:17:58.627 --> 00:18:00.293
So I found a place out in the desert,

