00:18:03.045 --> 00:18:04.413
Putting the barrel in my mouth,

461
00:18:04.413 --> 00:18:06.526
what it would feel like to prepare myself.

462
00:18:06.526 --> 00:18:09.163
It's in a sense something I didn't really wanna do,

463
00:18:09.163 --> 00:18:11.683
but it was a means to an end.

464
00:18:13.526 --> 00:18:14.811
<v ->So,</v>

