00:18:23.185 --> 00:18:24.394
the next day.

469
00:18:24.394 --> 00:18:26.468
<v ->Yeah, it was something that was gonna come very quickly</v>

470
00:18:26.468 --> 00:18:29.565
and I knew that I would not reach my 46th birthday,

471
00:18:29.565 --> 00:18:30.982
which was August 20th.

472
00:18:30.982 --> 00:18:32.374
And I had already committed to that,

473
00:18:32.374 --> 00:18:35.665
that I would not go beyond 45 in this world.

474
00:18:35.665 --> 00:18:38.411
This is something that was helping me to set a deadline.

475
00:18:38.411 --> 00:18:40.458
Something that I could meet.

476
00:18:40.882 --> 00:18:43.022
Then I remember it was,

477
00:18:43.022 --> 00:18:46.707
I believe the 26th of July.

478
00:18:46.912 --> 00:18:49.348
I was sitting in my bedroom at my desk, on the computer,

479
00:18:49.348 --> 00:18:52.708
and I just felt this need to find some relief.

480
00:18:52.708 --> 00:18:54.992
So I got on Conscious Media Network again.

481
00:18:54.992 --> 00:18:55.975
(chuckling)

482
00:18:55.975 --> 00:18:57.524
Because I had found so much relief there

