00:19:16.715 --> 00:19:19.539
but I felt this nudge, take a look at it anyhow.

492
00:19:19.539 --> 00:19:21.771
So I said, okay, I'll look at it.

493
00:19:21.771 --> 00:19:23.148
<v ->And it was one of the newest ones</v>

