00:19:25.773 --> 00:19:27.995
And it wasn't the genre that I was accustomed to.

497
00:19:27.995 --> 00:19:29.712
I would go for the heart and soul,

498
00:19:29.712 --> 00:19:33.678
the things that would lift me up and make me feel good.

